!!!
html
  head
    title Zeke Sikelianos, Internet Designer/Developer
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")

    link(href='//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,700|PT+Serif:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='/assets/styles.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

    script(src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js")
    script(src="/assets/app.js")

  body

    //- a#toggle

    #toc
      - each section in public.resume._data.sections
        a.section(href="#"+section.slug)= section.name
        ul.things
          - each thing in public.resume._data[section.slug]
            li
              a(href="#"+thing.slug)= thing.name

    #images
      - each image in public.assets.images._data
        a(href=image.url title=image.title)
          img(src=image.urls.medium alt=image.title)

    section.first
      article

        img(src="/assets/images/anthropomorphs2.png")

        aside
          h1 Zeke<br /> Sikelianos

          :markdown
            I'm a designer and software developer in the [San Francisco](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emperor_Norton) Bay Area. I work at [Heroku](http://heroku.com), where I design and build open-source tools to help creative people build the Internet. I believe [information wants to be free](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hacker_ethic), and that you can create beautiful things with computers.

          :markdown
            Find me on [Twitter](http://twitter.com/zeke),
            [GitHub](http://github.com/zeke), and [Cargo](http://cargocollective.com/zeke).

    section
      article

        h2
          a(id="projects" href="#projects") Projects

    section
      article

        ul
          - each project in public.resume._data.projects
            li(id=project.slug)
              h3
                a(href=project.website)= project.name
                a.permalink(href="#"+project.slug) #
              p= project.description

        h2
          a(id="jobs" href="#jobs") Places I've Worked

        ul
          - each job in public.resume._data.jobs
            li(id=job.slug)
              h3
                a(href=job.website)= job.name
                em= job.location
                a.permalink(href="#"+job.slug) #

              p= job.description
              p.paltry
                = job.start
                = " - "
                = job.end

        h2
          a(id="schools" href="#schools") Schools I've Attended

        ul
          - each school in public.resume._data.schools
            li(id=school.slug)
              h3
                a(href=school.website)= school.name
                em=  school.location
                a.permalink(href="#"+school.slug) #
              p= school.description
              p.paltry
                = school.start
                = " - "
                = school.end

        h2
          a(id="fin" href="#fin") Keep in Touch

        :markdown
          I'm [zeke on Twitter](http://twitter.com/zeke) and
          [zeke on GitHub](http://github.com/zeke), and my email address is [zeke@sikelianos.com](mailto:zeke@sikelianos.com). Please send me something!

        :markdown
          Lastly, I'm starting an email newsletter. I know it sounds a bit old-fashioned but I want to give it a try. Please subscribe if you're my mom, or one of my siblings, or a friend, or even if you're a stranger interested in my work. I promise not to spam you or share your email address with any baddies.

        form(action='//sikelianos.us6.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=eb1baf73af6cc872dd06ed858&id=7f60b90055', method='post', name='mc-embedded-subscribe-form', target='_blank', novalidate='novalidate')
          input(type='text', value='', name='FNAME', placeholder='First name' autcorrect="off")
          input(type='text', value='', name='LNAME', placeholder='Last name' tabindex=2)
          input(type='email', value='', name='EMAIL', placeholder='Email address', required='required' tabindex=3)

          input.honey(type='text', name='b_eb1baf73af6cc872dd06ed858_7f60b90055', tabindex='-1', value='' style="width:0;height:0;opacity:0;")
          input(type='submit', value="Subscribe to the Imaginary Newsletter", name='subscribe' tabindex=4)


      footer
        :markdown
          [♥‿♥](http://asciiface.zeke.xxx/)
